00:01:13.699 --> 00:01:15.000
&gt;&gt; WHAT ARE YOU ASKING ABOUT THE

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:16.267
DOLLARS FOR, ANYWAY?

00:01:16.267 --> 00:01:17.002
&gt;&gt; DON’T TELL ME YOU’RE

00:01:17.002 --> 00:01:18.570
SERIOUSLY THINKING ABOUT JOINING

00:01:18.570 --> 00:01:19.570
THE DOLLARS.

00:01:19.570 --> 00:01:21.339
&gt;&gt; WHAT THE HELL KIND OF ANSWER

00:01:21.339 --> 00:01:22.507
IS THAT?!

00:01:22.507 --> 00:01:23.608
&gt;&gt; WHY IS SOME OTHER BODY

00:01:23.608 --> 00:01:25.376
WALKING AROUND WITH MY HEAD ON

00:01:25.376 --> 00:01:25.876
ITS SHOULDERS?

00:01:25.876 --> 00:01:26.944
&gt;&gt; MAYBE YOUR HEAD STUMBLED

00:01:26.944 --> 00:01:27.978
ACROSS A FRESH CORPSE.

00:01:27.978 --> 00:01:28.946
&gt;&gt; THIS’LL BE FUN.

00:01:28.946 --> 00:01:30.248
THIS’LL BE FUN.

00:01:30.248 --> 00:01:31.282
THIS’LL BE FUN.

00:01:31.282 --> 00:01:32.383
&gt;&gt; IF THE POLICE COME ACROSS

00:01:32.383 --> 00:01:33.518
THAT THING BEFORE WE DO,

00:01:33.518 --> 00:01:34.985
THAT WON’T WORK OUT WELL FOR US.

00:01:34.985 --> 00:01:36.486
I WANT HER DEAD OR ALIVE.

00:01:36.486 --> 00:01:37.622
IF YOU HAVE ANY TROUBLE BRINGING

00:01:37.622 --> 00:01:38.823
HER BACK, THEN DISPOSE OF HER.

00:01:38.823 --> 00:01:41.826
&gt;&gt; ♪ [singing in Japanese] ♪

00:01:41.826 --> 00:01:49.866
♪ ♪

00:02:05.448 --> 00:02:07.350
&gt;&gt; [sighs]

00:02:07.350 --> 00:02:08.484
I DON’T KNOW.

00:02:08.484 --> 00:02:09.385
THINGS ARE KIND OF TIGHT THIS

00:02:09.385 --> 00:02:11.620
MONTH.

00:02:11.620 --> 00:02:12.788
ALL RIGHT, I ALSO HAVE TO GET A

00:02:12.788 --> 00:02:14.523
SPONGE FOR THE KITCHEN.

00:02:14.523 --> 00:02:17.826
&gt;&gt; THANK YOU, HAVE A NICE DAY!

00:02:17.826 --> 00:02:18.894
&gt;&gt; [sighs]

00:02:18.894 --> 00:02:19.828
[horse neighing]

00:02:19.828 --> 00:02:21.729
THE BLACK BIKE!

00:02:26.401 --> 00:02:27.402
IT SHOULD BE RIGHT AROUND THAT

00:02:27.402 --> 00:02:29.604
CORNER...

00:02:29.604 --> 00:02:32.807
[exclamations]

00:02:35.910 --> 00:02:36.811
I’M SO SORRY!

00:02:36.811 --> 00:02:40.781
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

00:02:40.781 --> 00:02:43.617
YOU’RE THAT...

00:02:43.617 --> 00:02:44.551
&gt;&gt; SAVE ME!

00:02:44.551 --> 00:02:47.654
&gt;&gt; HUH? HUH?

00:02:47.654 --> 00:02:49.055
&gt;&gt; [gasps]

00:02:49.055 --> 00:02:51.291
&gt;&gt; SAVE ME!

00:03:02.068 --> 00:03:04.437
&gt;&gt; HEY!

00:03:30.395 --> 00:03:31.896
[girls shrieking]

00:03:31.896 --> 00:03:32.697
&gt;&gt; THE RIDER.

00:03:32.697 --> 00:03:33.431
&gt;&gt; THE BLACK RIDER!

00:03:33.431 --> 00:03:33.932
&gt;&gt; OH, MY GOD.

00:03:33.932 --> 00:03:34.799
THIS IS SO COOL!

00:03:34.799 --> 00:03:35.834
&gt;&gt; I CAN’T BELIEVE IT.

00:03:35.834 --> 00:03:37.035
I JUST TOTALLY GOT ITS PICTURE!

00:03:37.035 --> 00:03:38.002
&gt;&gt; I’M SO POSTING THIS.

00:03:38.002 --> 00:03:39.437
[giggling]

00:03:42.973 --> 00:03:44.608
&gt;&gt; HUH.

00:03:44.608 --> 00:03:45.776
SO YOU JUST BUMPED INTO THIS

00:03:45.776 --> 00:03:46.877
BEAUTIFUL GIRL ON THE STREET

00:03:46.877 --> 00:03:47.878
WHO LOST HER MEMORIES AND IS

00:03:47.878 --> 00:03:49.513
BEING CHASED BY THE BLACK RIDER.

00:03:49.513 --> 00:03:50.614
AND BY THE TIME I GET HERE,

00:03:50.614 --> 00:03:51.749
THIS CHICK HAS ALREADY GONE TO

00:03:51.749 --> 00:03:52.205
SLEEP.

00:03:52.205 --> 00:03:53.083
AND YOU REALLY THINK I’M GONNA

00:03:53.083 --> 00:03:54.652
BELIEVE THIS WILD-ASS STORY

00:03:54.652 --> 00:03:55.819
YOU’VE CONCOCTED?

00:03:55.819 --> 00:03:56.954
&gt;&gt; I’M TELLING YOU, MAN, IT’S

00:03:56.954 --> 00:03:58.455
REALLY THE TRUTH.

00:03:58.455 --> 00:03:59.522
&gt;&gt; IF THIS TOOK PLACE IN THE

00:03:59.522 --> 00:04:00.157
MORNING AND IT MADE YOU LATE

00:04:00.157 --> 00:04:03.093
FOR SCHOOL, IT’D BE WAY BETTER.

00:04:03.093 --> 00:04:04.126
OH, AND IF SHE WERE A TRANSFER

00:04:04.126 --> 00:04:06.463
STUDENT TOO, GENIUS!

00:04:06.463 --> 00:04:07.129
NO, NO, WAIT.

00:04:07.129 --> 00:04:08.431
SHE’S A PRINCESS AND YOUR

00:04:08.431 --> 00:04:09.398
LONG-LOST FRIEND.

00:04:09.398 --> 00:04:10.900
NOW THAT’S PERFECT!

00:04:10.900 --> 00:04:12.168
TELL ME, ARE YOU CATCHING MY

00:04:12.168 --> 00:04:14.136
WITTY SARCASM HERE OR NOT?

00:04:14.136 --> 00:04:15.137
&gt;&gt; YEAH, BUT IF YOU HAVE TO

00:04:15.137 --> 00:04:16.672
EXPLAIN IT, THEN IT’S NOT SO

00:04:16.672 --> 00:04:17.406
WITTY.

00:04:17.406 --> 00:04:18.007
[sighs]

00:04:18.007 --> 00:04:18.975
SHE SAYS SHE CAN’T REMEMBER

00:04:18.975 --> 00:04:20.709
ANYTHING AND SHE WON’T LET ME GO

00:04:20.709 --> 00:04:21.477
TO THE POLICE.

00:04:21.477 --> 00:04:22.778
I DON’T KNOW WHAT ELSE I SHOULD

00:04:22.778 --> 00:04:24.112
DO.

00:04:24.112 --> 00:04:26.782
&gt;&gt; HMM, YOU’LL JUST HAVE TO KEEP

00:04:26.782 --> 00:04:29.050
AN EYE ON HER.

00:04:29.050 --> 00:04:30.185
LET HER SLEEP FOR NOW.

00:04:30.185 --> 00:04:31.620
AND THEN TOMORROW, WHEN SHE

00:04:31.620 --> 00:04:33.054
WAKES UP, SEE IF SHE FEELS ANY

00:04:33.054 --> 00:04:33.955
DIFFERENT.

00:04:33.955 --> 00:04:35.156
&gt;&gt; YEAH.

00:04:35.156 --> 00:04:36.925
&gt;&gt; ALL RIGHT, SEE YA TOMORROW.

00:04:36.925 --> 00:04:37.893
&gt;&gt; COOL.

00:04:37.893 --> 00:04:40.028
THANKS FOR COMING SO LATE.

00:04:44.499 --> 00:04:45.800
THE BLACK RIDER KNOWS MY FACE

00:04:45.800 --> 00:04:47.502
NOW.

00:04:47.502 --> 00:04:48.969
IF THAT URBAN LEGEND IS ACTUALLY

00:04:48.969 --> 00:04:51.038
TRUE...

00:04:51.038 --> 00:04:52.206
WHAT IF THAT THING COMES AFTER

00:04:52.206 --> 00:04:52.940
ME?

00:04:52.940 --> 00:04:56.944
WHAT AM I GONNA DO?

00:04:56.944 --> 00:04:58.212
I USED TO HATE MY ORDINARY

00:04:58.212 --> 00:04:59.813
LIFE.

00:04:59.813 --> 00:05:01.915
&gt;&gt; all: GOOD MORNING.

00:05:03.683 --> 00:05:04.884
&gt;&gt; I WANTED MY LIFE TO BE

00:05:04.884 --> 00:05:08.154
DIFFERENT THAN EVERYONE ELSE’S.

00:05:08.154 --> 00:05:09.455
I GUESS THAT’S ONE OF THE

00:05:09.455 --> 00:05:10.523
REASONS WHY I’M LETTING HER

00:05:10.523 --> 00:05:12.658
STAY HERE.

00:05:12.658 --> 00:05:13.692
THERE’S ONE THING I DIDN’T

00:05:13.692 --> 00:05:17.530
TELL MASAOMI ABOUT--HER SCAR.

00:05:17.530 --> 00:05:18.831
IT’S ALMOST AS IF SOMEONE

00:05:18.831 --> 00:05:20.199
SAWED OFF HER HEAD...

00:05:20.199 --> 00:05:24.036
AND THEN SEWED IT BACK ON AGAIN.

00:05:24.036 --> 00:05:25.070
&gt;&gt; WE HAVE AN ANNOUNCEMENT FROM

00:05:25.070 --> 00:05:26.605
THE STUDENT STORE.

00:05:26.605 --> 00:05:28.040
THEY ARE CURRENTLY SOLD OUT OF

00:05:28.040 --> 00:05:29.541
THE JUMBO MELON BREAD...

00:05:29.541 --> 00:05:30.843
&gt;&gt; YO, MIKADO!

00:05:30.843 --> 00:05:32.044
HOW’S THAT SLEEPING BEAUTY YOU

00:05:32.044 --> 00:05:33.946
GOT STASHED AT YOUR PLACE?

00:05:33.946 --> 00:05:34.947
&gt;&gt; WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

00:05:34.947 --> 00:05:35.613
SHH! SHH!

00:05:35.613 --> 00:05:36.681
&gt;&gt; WHAT? YOU GOT SOME CHICK

00:05:36.681 --> 00:05:37.215
STAYING WITH YOU?

00:05:37.215 --> 00:05:38.150
&gt;&gt; I’D TRY TO KEEP THAT ON

00:05:38.150 --> 00:05:39.084
THE DOWN-LOW TOO.

00:05:39.084 --> 00:05:40.185
&gt;&gt; CHECK IT OUT.

00:05:40.185 --> 00:05:41.553
HE WAS JUST ROUNDING A CORNER

00:05:41.553 --> 00:05:43.087
AND BUMPS INTO A CUTIE WITH

00:05:43.087 --> 00:05:44.489
AMNESIA WHO’S BEING CHASED BY

00:05:44.489 --> 00:05:45.557
BAD GUYS.

00:05:45.557 --> 00:05:46.958
AND WHO’S SHE LIVING WITH NOW?

00:05:46.958 --> 00:05:48.860
THIS GUY.

00:05:48.860 --> 00:05:50.227
&gt;&gt; YEAH, NO WAY.

00:05:50.227 --> 00:05:51.662
KIRIGAMINE’S JUST MAKING THAT

00:05:51.662 --> 00:05:52.764
SHIT UP.

00:05:52.764 --> 00:05:54.966
&gt;&gt; NO, IT’S RYUGAMINE.

00:05:54.966 --> 00:05:56.100
&gt;&gt; HEY, DOES SOMEONE WANNA BUY

00:05:56.100 --> 00:05:56.833
MY LUNCH TICKETS?

00:05:56.833 --> 00:05:57.768
&gt;&gt; REALLY?

00:05:57.768 --> 00:05:58.835
&gt;&gt; [laughs nervously]

00:05:58.835 --> 00:06:00.070
&gt;&gt; SEE?

00:06:00.070 --> 00:06:01.071
NOTHING TO WORRY ABOUT BECAUSE

00:06:01.071 --> 00:06:03.073
NO ONE BELIEVES IT.

00:06:03.073 --> 00:06:04.975
SO HOW’S THE HOTTIE?

00:06:04.975 --> 00:06:05.842
&gt;&gt; I DON’T KNOW.

00:06:05.842 --> 00:06:06.710
SHE WAS STILL ASLEEP WHEN I

00:06:06.710 --> 00:06:07.243
LEFT.

00:06:07.243 --> 00:06:08.211
&gt;&gt; SLEEPING BEAUTY’S PRETTY

00:06:08.211 --> 00:06:09.980
SLEEPY.

00:06:09.980 --> 00:06:10.646
ALL RIGHT.

00:06:10.646 --> 00:06:11.948
LET’S GET TO THE POINT.

00:06:11.948 --> 00:06:12.748
&gt;&gt; WHAT POINT?

00:06:12.748 --> 00:06:14.084
&gt;&gt; YEAH, THE POINT AS TO WHY I’M

00:06:14.084 --> 00:06:16.052
MACKIN’ DOWN IN FOURTH PERIOD.

00:06:16.052 --> 00:06:17.053
IT’S SO THAT I CAN FREE MYSELF

00:06:17.053 --> 00:06:20.022
UP ON THE LUNCH BREAK.

00:06:20.022 --> 00:06:22.091
&gt;&gt; THE DOLLARS POLL?

00:06:22.091 --> 00:06:23.526
&gt;&gt; DUDE, THIS IS LIKE THE HOT

00:06:23.526 --> 00:06:25.861
TOPIC RIGHT NOW IN OUR CLASS.

00:06:25.861 --> 00:06:26.896
THESE DOLLARS ARE TOTALLY

00:06:26.896 --> 00:06:28.197
SHROUDED IN MYSTERY.

00:06:28.197 --> 00:06:29.699
SO IF YOU SAW SOMEONE AND

00:06:29.699 --> 00:06:31.266
THOUGHT, "THAT DUDE SO LOOKS

00:06:31.266 --> 00:06:32.167
LIKE HE’S IN THE DOLLARS,"

00:06:32.167 --> 00:06:34.269
THEN FIND HIS NAME ON THE LIST

00:06:34.269 --> 00:06:35.770
AND VOTE FOR HIM!

00:06:35.770 --> 00:06:37.038
&gt;&gt; WOW, SOME PEOPLE ARE

00:06:37.038 --> 00:06:38.607
GETTIN’ A LOT OF VOTES.

00:06:38.607 --> 00:06:39.641
&gt;&gt; YOU CAN VOTE FOR AS MANY

00:06:39.641 --> 00:06:41.576
PEOPLE AS YOU WANT.

00:06:41.576 --> 00:06:42.076
&gt;&gt; HEY!

00:06:42.076 --> 00:06:44.178
THAT TAKIGUCHI GUY FROM 1D HAS

00:06:44.178 --> 00:06:46.247
JUST RECEIVED ONE VOTE SO FAR.

00:06:46.247 --> 00:06:48.016
&gt;&gt; THANK YOU FOR NOTICING.

00:06:48.016 --> 00:06:49.083
THAT’S RIGHT.

00:06:49.083 --> 00:06:50.118
ONE VOTE...

00:06:50.118 --> 00:06:51.052
FROM NONE OTHER THAN YOURS

00:06:51.052 --> 00:06:52.620
TRULY.

00:06:52.620 --> 00:06:54.155
SEE, ME AND THAT GUY HAVE GYM

00:06:54.155 --> 00:06:56.290
CLASS TOGETHER, AND I WAS LIKE,

00:06:56.290 --> 00:06:58.192
"YEAH, THAT DUDE’S GOTTA BE IN

00:06:58.192 --> 00:06:59.026
THE DOLLARS, MM-HMM."

00:06:59.026 --> 00:07:00.661
&gt;&gt; WHAT MAKES YOU THINK THAT?

00:07:00.661 --> 00:07:03.163
&gt;&gt; HUNCH.

00:07:03.163 --> 00:07:04.164
&gt;&gt; [laughs]

00:07:04.164 --> 00:07:05.799
&gt;&gt; AND NOW I’M OFF TO FIND OUT

00:07:05.799 --> 00:07:06.700
FOR SURE.

00:07:06.700 --> 00:07:08.635
&gt;&gt; W-WAIT A SEC.

00:07:08.635 --> 00:07:10.103
&gt;&gt; EXCUSE ME!

00:07:10.103 --> 00:07:12.205
IS RYOU TAKIGUCHI AROUND NOW?

00:07:12.205 --> 00:07:13.606
&gt;&gt; HUH?

00:07:13.606 --> 00:07:14.741
&gt;&gt; HE’S NOT HERE.

00:07:14.741 --> 00:07:16.209
&gt;&gt; DID HE GO TO EAT?

00:07:16.209 --> 00:07:17.877
&gt;&gt; BET HE’S UP ON THE ROOF.

00:07:17.877 --> 00:07:18.911
THAT’S WHERE HE USUALLY HANGS

00:07:18.911 --> 00:07:21.280
OUT ON LUNCH BREAK.

00:07:21.280 --> 00:07:22.982
&gt;&gt; I BET HE WENT UP THERE TO

00:07:22.982 --> 00:07:24.183
SMOKE A STOGIE.

00:07:24.183 --> 00:07:25.351
&gt;&gt; ARE YOU REALLY SURE WE

00:07:25.351 --> 00:07:26.619
SHOULD GO UP HERE?

00:07:26.619 --> 00:07:27.619
WE MIGHT BE HEADING INTO A

00:07:27.619 --> 00:07:28.654
ROUGH CROWD.

00:07:28.654 --> 00:07:30.189
&gt;&gt; DUDE, I’M JOKING.

00:07:30.189 --> 00:07:31.057
THE ONLY KIDS WHO SMOKE CIGS

00:07:31.057 --> 00:07:33.025
ON ROOFTOPS ARE THE ONES IN SOME

00:07:33.025 --> 00:07:34.193
CHEESY-ASS MANGA.

00:07:34.193 --> 00:07:36.061
YEAH, BUT WE JUST GONNA GO UP TO

00:07:36.061 --> 00:07:37.229
HIM AND SAY, "HEY, ARE YOU IN

00:07:37.229 --> 00:07:38.230
THE DOLLARS?"

00:07:38.230 --> 00:07:39.164
HE’S NOT GONNA TELL US THE

00:07:39.164 --> 00:07:41.032
TRUTH ABOUT SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

00:07:41.032 --> 00:07:42.668
&gt;&gt; YOU JUST LEAVE THAT TO ME.

00:07:42.668 --> 00:07:46.204
I’VE GOT A PLAN.

00:07:46.204 --> 00:07:48.239
LET’S SEE...

00:07:48.239 --> 00:07:49.875
THERE.

00:07:49.875 --> 00:07:52.310
&gt;&gt; HE--HE’S SMOKING...

00:07:52.310 --> 00:07:53.678
&gt;&gt; WHAT DO YA KNOW, IT’S

00:07:53.678 --> 00:07:55.180
TAKIGUCHI.

00:07:55.180 --> 00:07:56.147
YO.

00:07:56.147 --> 00:07:57.181
&gt;&gt; HEY.

00:07:57.181 --> 00:07:58.182
&gt;&gt; HUH.

00:07:58.182 --> 00:08:00.317
OH, COOL, YOU’RE WRITING A SONG.

00:08:00.317 --> 00:08:02.853
&gt;&gt; UH, YEAH, I AM.

00:08:02.853 --> 00:08:04.121
SO WHAT’S GOIN’ ON?

00:08:04.121 --> 00:08:05.222
YOU GUYS NEED SOMETHING?

00:08:05.222 --> 00:08:07.057
&gt;&gt; I GOT A QUESTION.

00:08:07.057 --> 00:08:08.258
&gt;&gt; GO FOR IT.

00:08:08.258 --> 00:08:09.693
&gt;&gt; [clears throat]

00:08:09.693 --> 00:08:11.128
YOU A MEMBER OF THE DOLLARS OR

00:08:11.128 --> 00:08:11.795
NOT?

00:08:11.795 --> 00:08:13.397
&gt;&gt; MASAOMI, WHAT ARE YOU--

00:08:13.397 --> 00:08:14.331
&gt;&gt; YEAH, I’M IN WITH THEM.

00:08:14.331 --> 00:08:15.199
&gt;&gt; AAHH!

00:08:15.199 --> 00:08:17.234
&gt;&gt; THOUGHT SO.

00:08:17.234 --> 00:08:19.168
IN FACT, I HAD NO DOUBT AT ALL.

00:08:19.168 --> 00:08:23.039
SEE? MY INSTINCTS: PERFECT.

00:08:23.039 --> 00:08:24.941
OH, THIS GUY HERE’S AN OLD

00:08:24.941 --> 00:08:26.743
FRIEND OF MINE.

00:08:26.743 --> 00:08:28.777
&gt;&gt; YEAH, I’M MIKADO RYUGAMINE.

00:08:28.777 --> 00:08:30.146
&gt;&gt; OH, YOU’RE THAT GUY.

00:08:30.146 --> 00:08:31.080
YOU’RE FAMOUS.

00:08:31.080 --> 00:08:32.748
&gt;&gt; HUH? I AM?

00:08:32.748 --> 00:08:33.949
&gt;&gt; JUST YOUR NAME.

00:08:33.949 --> 00:08:35.384
&gt;&gt; OH.

00:08:35.384 --> 00:08:36.419
&gt;&gt; WANT SOME?

00:08:36.419 --> 00:08:38.286
&gt;&gt; SURE, THANK YOU.

00:08:38.286 --> 00:08:39.221
&gt;&gt; HMM?

00:08:39.221 --> 00:08:43.291
&gt;&gt; THANKS, MAN.

00:08:43.291 --> 00:08:44.827
&gt;&gt; SO, TAKIGUCHI, I GOT A

00:08:44.827 --> 00:08:45.293
QUESTION.

00:08:45.293 --> 00:08:46.128
&gt;&gt; HMM?

00:08:46.128 --> 00:08:47.863
&gt;&gt; WHAT MADE YOU JOIN THE

00:08:47.863 --> 00:08:48.763
DOLLARS?

00:08:48.763 --> 00:08:50.265
&gt;&gt; HUH?

00:08:50.265 --> 00:08:51.966
HMM.

00:08:51.966 --> 00:08:53.000
I’M NOT REALLY SURE EXACTLY

00:08:53.000 --> 00:08:56.070
WHY I DECIDED TO DO IT.

00:08:56.070 --> 00:08:58.039
I THINK IT WAS SIX MONTHS AGO.

00:08:58.039 --> 00:08:59.674
I GOT AN EMAIL FROM SOME GUY I

00:08:59.674 --> 00:09:00.808
DIDN’T EVEN KNOW.

00:09:00.808 --> 00:09:02.209
HE MENTIONED THE DOLLARS AND

00:09:02.209 --> 00:09:03.244
SAID THEY DIDN’T HAVE ANY KIND

00:09:03.244 --> 00:09:05.446
OF RULES OR CONDITIONS.

00:09:05.446 --> 00:09:06.814
MY FIRST THOUGHT WAS, YEAH,

00:09:06.814 --> 00:09:07.915
RIGHT.

00:09:07.915 --> 00:09:08.882
BUT THEN I THOUGHT, IF THERE

00:09:08.882 --> 00:09:10.117
WAS A GROUP LIKE THAT, I’D

00:09:10.117 --> 00:09:13.287
WANT TO BE A PART OF IT.

00:09:13.287 --> 00:09:15.456
TRUTH IS, LAST THING I WANT IS

00:09:15.456 --> 00:09:17.157
TO BE BOSSED AROUND OR VICE

00:09:17.157 --> 00:09:18.992
VERSA.

00:09:18.992 --> 00:09:20.293
&gt;&gt; SO, WHAT ARE THE DOLLARS

00:09:20.293 --> 00:09:20.961
LIKE?

00:09:20.961 --> 00:09:22.128
FILL US IN.

00:09:22.128 --> 00:09:23.697
&gt;&gt; WELL, GUESS I’D SAY

00:09:23.697 --> 00:09:26.066
TRANSPARENT, AS IN NO COLOR.

00:09:26.066 --> 00:09:27.233
&gt;&gt; TRANSPARENT?

