&gt;&gt; SO THEN, YOU’RE TELLING US

00:09:49.754 --> 00:09:51.356
THAT YOU LIKE THE DOLLARS?

00:09:51.356 --> 00:09:52.291
&gt;&gt; YEAH.

00:09:52.291 --> 00:09:53.392
&gt;&gt; YOU EVER GET TOGETHER WITH

00:09:53.392 --> 00:09:54.393
THE OTHER MEMBERS?

