JUST BY ACCIDENT.

00:10:03.301 --> 00:10:04.402
IF YOU THINK, "I BET HE’S WITH

00:10:04.402 --> 00:10:05.904
THE DOLLARS," TURNS OUT THEY

00:10:05.904 --> 00:10:07.005
USUALLY ARE.

00:10:07.005 --> 00:10:08.139
&gt;&gt; HOW CAN YOU TELL BY LOOKING

00:10:08.139 --> 00:10:08.906
AT THEM?

