&gt;&gt; I DON’T KNOW.

00:10:09.473 --> 00:10:10.408
IT’S HARD TO EXPLAIN.

00:10:10.408 --> 00:10:11.475
JUST ASK ’EM.

00:10:11.475 --> 00:10:12.876
