[alarm rings]

00:10:18.315 --> 00:10:19.316
WELL, THAT BLOWS.

00:10:19.316 --> 00:10:22.419
&gt;&gt; SEE YA, SUCKERS!

00:10:22.419 --> 00:10:23.787
&gt;&gt; ONCE I FOUND OUT THAT

00:10:23.787 --> 00:10:25.022
TAKIGUCHI WAS PART OF THE

