DOLLARS, I SWORE I’D KEEP IT A

00:10:27.090 --> 00:10:29.892
SECRET AND NEVER TELL ANYONE.

00:10:29.892 --> 00:10:31.027
I DON’T KNOW HIM, BUT I’M

00:10:31.027 --> 00:10:32.329
GUESSING HE WOULDN’T WANT

00:10:32.329 --> 00:10:33.430
PEOPLE TO MAKE A BIG DEAL OUT

00:10:33.430 --> 00:10:34.230
OF IT.

