&gt;&gt; ALL RIGHT, CLASS.

00:10:35.197 --> 00:10:36.098
&gt;&gt; I FIGURE IF ANYONE WANTS

00:10:36.098 --> 00:10:38.167
TO KNOW, THEY CAN ASK HIM.

00:10:38.167 --> 00:10:40.202
STAND.

00:10:40.202 --> 00:10:42.004
BOW.

