&gt;&gt; OKAY, THAT’S IT FOR THE CLASS

00:10:48.410 --> 00:10:50.312
REPS MEETING.

00:10:50.312 --> 00:10:51.880
&gt;&gt; I WONDER IF MASAOMI’S HALL

00:10:51.880 --> 00:10:53.415
MONITOR MEETING IS OVER.

00:10:53.415 --> 00:10:54.816
&gt;&gt; HMM.

00:10:54.816 --> 00:10:55.851
WELL, IF IT ISN’T, IT SHOULD

00:10:55.851 --> 00:10:57.252
BE OVER PRETTY SOON.

00:10:57.252 --> 00:11:01.990
[girls giggling]

00:11:01.990 --> 00:11:03.291
&gt;&gt; MIKA HARIMA, THE GIRL WHO

00:11:03.291 --> 00:11:05.526
WAS STALKING SEIJI YAGIRI, HAS

00:11:05.526 --> 00:11:07.062
BEEN MISSING EVEN BEFORE SCHOOL

00:11:07.062 --> 00:11:08.028
STARTED.

