ON YOUR FRIEND MIKA?

00:11:11.299 --> 00:11:13.901
&gt;&gt; NO. NOTHING.

00:11:13.901 --> 00:11:16.804
&gt;&gt; HEY, MIKADO!

00:11:16.804 --> 00:11:18.138
MASAOMI SAID FOR YOU TO GO

