IT’S ALL GOOD.

00:11:27.414 --> 00:11:30.484
SEE YA!

00:11:30.484 --> 00:11:32.852
&gt;&gt; WELL, THEN, ARE YOU READY

00:11:32.852 --> 00:11:33.887
TO GO?

00:11:33.887 --> 00:11:39.058
&gt;&gt; SURE.

00:11:39.058 --> 00:11:40.359
&gt;&gt; I WONDER WHAT’S SO

00:11:40.359 --> 00:11:41.594
IMPORTANT THAT MASAOMI WOULD

00:11:41.594 --> 00:11:43.229
STAY LATE TO ARGUE ABOUT IT.

00:11:43.229 --> 00:11:44.230
YOU KNOW, IT’S PROBABLY JUST

00:11:44.230 --> 00:11:44.963
LIKE CLOTHES AND...

00:11:44.963 --> 00:11:47.133
&gt;&gt; MIKADO!

00:11:47.133 --> 00:11:48.133
DON’T SCREW IT UP WITH THAT

00:11:48.133 --> 00:11:49.935
FINE CHICA.

00:11:49.935 --> 00:11:51.036
AND NEXT TIME YOU HAVE TO

00:11:51.036 --> 00:11:52.905
INTRODUCE ME.

00:11:52.905 --> 00:11:55.541
PEACE OUT. LATER!

00:11:55.541 --> 00:11:58.276
&gt;&gt; UH...

00:11:58.276 --> 00:12:00.212
UH, HE MEANT MISS FINECHICA.

00:12:00.212 --> 00:12:01.613
IT’S THIS FRENCH GIRL WE MET

00:12:01.613 --> 00:12:03.248
AT THAT RUSSIA SUSHI PLACE.

00:12:03.248 --> 00:12:05.517
AND UH, SH-SH-SHE’S GOT--GOT

00:12:05.517 --> 00:12:07.084
A NOSE RING!

