00:12:08.186 --> 00:12:09.587
ARGUING ABOUT, WHETHER OR NOT

00:12:09.587 --> 00:12:10.988
THEY SHOULD ALLOW NOSE RINGS AT

00:12:10.988 --> 00:12:11.556
SCHOOL.

00:12:11.556 --> 00:12:14.158
[laughs]

00:12:14.158 --> 00:12:15.927
&gt;&gt; YOU KNOW, I’VE KINDA KNOWN

00:12:15.927 --> 00:12:17.094
WHO YOU WERE LONG BEFORE YOU

00:12:17.094 --> 00:12:19.130
AND I EVEN MET IN CLASS.

00:12:19.130 --> 00:12:19.997
&gt;&gt; HUH?

00:12:19.997 --> 00:12:21.132
&gt;&gt; WHEN I CAME TO THE SCHOOL TO

00:12:21.132 --> 00:12:23.100
REGISTER, I SAW A LIST OF

00:12:23.100 --> 00:12:24.035
NAMES ON A DESK AS I WAS

