00:12:28.905 --> 00:12:29.973
THE GUY WITH THAT NAME WAS

00:12:29.973 --> 00:12:31.575
RIGHT NEXT TO ME.

00:12:31.575 --> 00:12:33.510
AND THEN NEXT THING I KNOW, HE

00:12:33.510 --> 00:12:35.111
AND I ENDED UP BEING CLASS REPS

00:12:35.111 --> 00:12:35.545
TOGETHER.

00:12:35.545 --> 00:12:36.246
&gt;&gt; WAIT A SECOND!

00:12:36.246 --> 00:12:37.247
ISN’T THIS SORT OF LIKE WHAT

00:12:37.247 --> 00:12:38.414
HER FRIEND MIKA DID TO THAT

00:12:38.414 --> 00:12:39.549
SEIJI GUY?

00:12:39.549 --> 00:12:41.884
OH, MAN. IS SHE A STALKER?

00:12:41.884 --> 00:12:43.353
HOLD ON, IF SHE’S CUTE, MAYBE

00:12:43.353 --> 00:12:44.920
IT’S OKAY.

00:12:44.920 --> 00:12:46.055
NO, NO, NO.

00:12:46.055 --> 00:12:47.122
THIS IS STILL BAD.

00:12:47.122 --> 00:12:51.527
IF SOMETHING HAPPENS...

00:12:51.527 --> 00:12:52.394
&gt;&gt; I WANT YOU NOW!

00:12:52.394 --> 00:12:54.597
&gt;&gt; SHE COULD TOTALLY STAB ME!

00:12:54.597 --> 00:12:55.898
OR SHE MIGHT EVEN SET MY PLACE

00:12:55.898 --> 00:12:57.266
ON FIRE!

