00:12:59.134 --> 00:13:00.970
PARENTS HOSTAGE?

00:13:00.970 --> 00:13:01.971
BUT IF SHE’S A GOOD PERSON,

00:13:01.971 --> 00:13:03.905
MAYBE I DON’T MIND HER STALKING

00:13:03.905 --> 00:13:04.939
ME.

00:13:04.939 --> 00:13:06.140
WHAT AM I SAYING?

00:13:06.140 --> 00:13:07.309
IF SHE’S STALKING ME, THEN SHE

00:13:07.309 --> 00:13:08.943
CAN’T BE A GOOD PERSON!

00:13:08.943 --> 00:13:10.612
&gt;&gt; I WAS JUST KIDDING.

00:13:10.612 --> 00:13:12.013
BESIDES, YOU WOULDN’T WANT

00:13:12.013 --> 00:13:13.281
SOMEONE LIKE ME HANGING AROUND

00:13:13.281 --> 00:13:14.683
ALL THE TIME.

00:13:14.683 --> 00:13:15.984
&gt;&gt; NO, I...

00:13:15.984 --> 00:13:17.551
&gt;&gt; I KNOW THAT SOUNDED WEIRD.

00:13:17.551 --> 00:13:18.586
BUT DON’T WORRY, I’M NOT A

00:13:18.586 --> 00:13:19.988
STALKER OR ANYTHING.

00:13:19.988 --> 00:13:21.555
&gt;&gt; NO, I DIDN’T--

00:13:21.555 --> 00:13:23.291
WELL, I...

00:13:23.291 --> 00:13:24.358
I’M SORRY.

00:13:24.358 --> 00:13:26.159
&gt;&gt; HUH. NO, IT’S FINE.

00:13:26.159 --> 00:13:27.461
I WAS THE ONE WHO STARTED IT BY

00:13:27.461 --> 00:13:28.429
TEASING YOU.

00:13:28.429 --> 00:13:32.132
THERE’S NO NEED TO APOLOGIZE.

00:13:32.132 --> 00:13:34.067
&gt;&gt; ALL RIGHT.

00:13:34.067 --> 00:13:36.569
WELL, LISTEN, I’M--I’M GLAD

00:13:36.569 --> 00:13:38.038
WE BECAME FRIENDS.

00:13:38.038 --> 00:13:39.506
&gt;&gt; I’M GLAD WE BECAME FRIENDS

00:13:39.506 --> 00:13:41.341
TOO.

00:13:47.213 --> 00:13:48.114
&gt;&gt; HUH?

00:13:48.114 --> 00:13:49.115
&gt;&gt; YEAH, IT’S BEEN A LOT OF FUN.

00:13:49.115 --> 00:13:50.049
&gt;&gt; [exclaims]

00:13:50.049 --> 00:13:51.083
TAKESHI, THAT’S HIM.

00:13:51.083 --> 00:13:55.487
THAT’S THE LOSER. LOOK!

00:13:55.487 --> 00:13:57.957
&gt;&gt; HUH?

00:13:57.957 --> 00:14:00.092
&gt;&gt; I WONDER WHO THE LOSER IS.

00:14:00.092 --> 00:14:02.294
IT’S NOT ME, RIGHT?

00:14:07.065 --> 00:14:08.299
&gt;&gt; I’M TALKIN’ TO YOU!

00:14:08.299 --> 00:14:09.468
DON’T IGNORE ME, YOU PATHETIC

00:14:09.468 --> 00:14:12.037
RUNT.

00:14:12.037 --> 00:14:14.172
&gt;&gt; WELL, JUST HOW DO I KNOW YOU?

00:14:14.172 --> 00:14:15.406
&gt;&gt; I’M THE ONE WHOSE CELL PHONE

00:14:15.406 --> 00:14:17.042
WAS SMASHED BY YOUR FREAKY

00:14:17.042 --> 00:14:18.409
FRIEND, SO I HAD TO GO AND BUY A

00:14:18.409 --> 00:14:19.644
NEW ONE.

00:14:19.644 --> 00:14:21.746
&gt;&gt; SORRY, BUT I REALLY HAVE NO

00:14:21.746 --> 00:14:24.482
IDEA WHAT YOU’RE TALKING ABOUT.

00:14:24.482 --> 00:14:27.452
OH.

00:14:27.452 --> 00:14:29.253
&gt;&gt; [growls]

00:14:29.253 --> 00:14:30.287
&gt;&gt; OH...

00:14:30.287 --> 00:14:31.455
&gt;&gt; THIS TRUE?

00:14:31.455 --> 00:14:32.222
YOU FRIENDS WITH THAT

00:14:32.222 --> 00:14:33.490
PUNK-ASS BITCH WHO WENT AND

00:14:33.490 --> 00:14:35.425
BUSTED UP MY GIRL’S CELL PHONE?

00:14:35.425 --> 00:14:37.194
&gt;&gt; WELL, I DON’T THINK HE

00:14:37.194 --> 00:14:38.695
AND I ARE REALLY FRIENDS.

00:14:38.695 --> 00:14:40.029
&gt;&gt; SO THEN WHAT IS HE, YOUR

00:14:40.029 --> 00:14:40.697
