00:14:50.239 --> 00:14:51.540
LESSON ABOUT WHERE YOU BELONG

00:14:51.540 --> 00:14:53.076
ON THE FOOD CHAIN.

00:14:53.076 --> 00:14:56.012
HUH?

00:14:56.012 --> 00:15:00.183
[groans]

