00:15:09.224 --> 00:15:11.026
AGAINST HITTING WOMEN?

00:15:11.026 --> 00:15:13.061
WHAT A CLEVER GIRL YOU ARE.

00:15:13.061 --> 00:15:14.362
I WOULD ASK YOU OUT.

00:15:14.362 --> 00:15:17.799
HOWEVER, YOU’RE SO NOT MY TYPE.

00:15:17.799 --> 00:15:21.403
NOW SCRAM!

00:15:21.403 --> 00:15:22.804
&gt;&gt; YOU’RE AN ASSHOLE!

00:15:22.804 --> 00:15:26.240
&gt;&gt; HAVE A NICE DAY!

00:15:26.240 --> 00:15:28.509
SO, MIKADO RYUGAMINE...

00:15:28.509 --> 00:15:29.677
I WAS LAYING LOW OUTSIDE THE

00:15:29.677 --> 00:15:31.212
SCHOOL’S FRONT GATE HOPING I’D

00:15:31.212 --> 00:15:33.547
RUN INTO YOU.

00:15:33.547 --> 00:15:36.150
I’D LIKE TO HAVE A LITTLE CHAT.

00:15:36.150 --> 00:15:38.252
BY THE WAY, WHAT’S THE BLACK

00:15:38.252 --> 00:15:40.120
RIDER DOING HERE?

00:15:44.658 --> 00:15:47.293
&gt;&gt; IT’S LOOKING FOR THAT GIRL.

00:15:47.293 --> 00:15:49.595
OH, GOSH. I FORGOT!

00:15:49.595 --> 00:15:51.197
I-I’M SORRY, BUT I REALLY

00:15:51.197 --> 00:15:52.232
GOTTA GO RIGHT NOW!

00:15:52.232 --> 00:15:55.568
BYE. SEE YOU TOMORROW, ANRI.

