00:16:04.376 --> 00:16:06.546
VROOM. VROOM. VROOM.

00:16:06.546 --> 00:16:07.512
VROOM.

00:16:07.512 --> 00:16:09.548
&gt;&gt; THIS IS SO BIZARRE.

