00:16:37.108 --> 00:16:39.277
HELLO? [laughs]

00:16:39.277 --> 00:16:41.545
ALWAYS HAPPY TO BE OF SERVICE.

00:16:41.545 --> 00:16:42.880
&gt;&gt; UM, THERE’S SOMETHING I WOULD

00:16:42.880 --> 00:16:45.816
LIKE TO ASK YOU.

