&gt;&gt; WHAT IS IT?

00:16:46.717 --> 00:16:50.153
&gt;&gt; SO IT CAN COMMUNICATE.

00:16:50.153 --> 00:16:52.122
WELL, I-I WAS JUST WONDERING

00:16:52.122 --> 00:16:54.524
WHAT YOU ARE.

00:17:00.830 --> 00:17:02.599
&gt;&gt; I’M LOOKING FOR A GIRL.

00:17:02.599 --> 00:17:03.900
SHE’S A RELATIVE OF MINE WHO’S

00:17:03.900 --> 00:17:04.734
GONE MISSING.

00:17:04.734 --> 00:17:05.868
I FOUND HER YESTERDAY, BUT THEN

00:17:05.868 --> 00:17:08.537
SHE RAN AWAY FOR SOME REASON.

00:17:08.537 --> 00:17:10.840
&gt;&gt; IT’S A TERRIBLE LIAR.

00:17:10.840 --> 00:17:13.275
UM, I’M SORRY, BUT I DON’T

00:17:13.275 --> 00:17:17.646
BELIEVE YOU.

00:17:17.646 --> 00:17:19.180
&gt;&gt; HOW MUCH DO YOU REALLY KNOW

00:17:19.180 --> 00:17:20.616
ABOUT ME?

00:17:20.616 --> 00:17:22.618
&gt;&gt; WELL, I-I JUST KNOW WHAT THE

00:17:22.618 --> 00:17:24.152
URBAN LEGEND SAYS--

00:17:24.152 --> 00:17:25.353
THAT YOU RIDE AROUND ON THIS

00:17:25.353 --> 00:17:26.621
BIKE WITH NO HEADLIGHT AND NO

00:17:26.621 --> 00:17:29.290
