00:17:32.860 --> 00:17:36.664
HEAD.

00:17:36.664 --> 00:17:37.832
&gt;&gt; AND DO YOU ACTUALLY BELIEVE

00:17:37.832 --> 00:17:41.401
THIS?

00:17:41.401 --> 00:17:42.803
&gt;&gt; YOU KNOW, YOU COULD ALWAYS

00:17:42.803 --> 00:17:44.772
SHOW ME WHAT’S INSIDE YOUR

00:17:44.772 --> 00:17:46.206
HELMET.

00:17:46.206 --> 00:17:47.507
THAT WAS PRETTY SHOCKING,

00:17:47.507 --> 00:17:48.308
EVEN FOR ME.

00:17:48.308 --> 00:17:49.309
I DIDN’T THINK I’D HAVE THE

00:17:49.309 --> 00:17:49.843
GUTS TO SAY THAT.

00:17:49.843 --> 00:17:50.810
&gt;&gt; PROMISE ME THAT YOU WON’T

00:17:50.810 --> 00:17:53.213
SCREAM?

00:17:53.213 --> 00:17:54.714
&gt;&gt; BUT AT THE SAME TIME, I

00:17:54.714 --> 00:17:56.216
FELT LIKE I’D BEEN WAITING FOR

00:17:56.216 --> 00:17:57.517
A MOMENT LIKE THIS TO OCCUR

00:17:57.517 --> 00:18:02.288
FOR YEARS.

00:18:02.288 --> 00:18:03.590
I STILL CAN’T DESCRIBE HOW I

00:18:03.590 --> 00:18:06.259
FELT AT THAT EXACT MOMENT.

00:18:06.259 --> 00:18:07.526
I JUST FOUND MYSELF THINKING,

00:18:07.526 --> 00:18:10.529
"I KNEW IT! I KNEW IT!", OVER

00:18:10.529 --> 00:18:13.299
AND OVER AGAIN.

00:18:13.299 --> 00:18:15.334
THANK YOU SO MUCH.

00:18:19.337 --> 00:18:20.906
AFTER THAT, THE BLACK RIDER

00:18:20.906 --> 00:18:22.575
TOLD ME EVERYTHING--LIKE THE

00:18:22.575 --> 00:18:23.976
REAL REASON IT WAS LOOKING FOR

00:18:23.976 --> 00:18:26.311
THAT GIRL YESTERDAY.

00:18:26.311 --> 00:18:27.412
IT TOLD ME IT WAS A DULLAHAN

00:18:27.412 --> 00:18:28.914
NAMED CELTY.

00:18:28.914 --> 00:18:29.948
THAT SHE’D COME TO JAPAN IN

00:18:29.948 --> 00:18:30.983
SEARCH OF HER HEAD THAT HAD BEEN

00:18:30.983 --> 00:18:32.217
STOLEN.

00:18:32.217 --> 00:18:33.685
AND WHEN CELTY SAW THE GIRL WITH

00:18:33.685 --> 00:18:35.487
STITCHES ON HER NECK, HER FACE

00:18:35.487 --> 00:18:37.955
LOOKED JUST LIKE HER OWN.

00:18:37.955 --> 00:18:38.890
NORMALLY, I WOULD NEVER BELIEVE

00:18:38.890 --> 00:18:40.892
A STORY LIKE THAT, BUT FOR

00:18:40.892 --> 00:18:42.827
SOME REASON, SITTING THERE WITH

00:18:42.827 --> 00:18:45.396
HER, I FELT LIKE I COULD.

00:18:45.396 --> 00:18:46.697
&gt;&gt; SO, ARE YOU FRIENDS WITH THIS

00:18:46.697 --> 00:18:47.631
GIRL?

00:18:47.631 --> 00:18:48.465
&gt;&gt; NO.

00:18:48.465 --> 00:18:49.666
ACTUALLY, YESTERDAY WAS THE

00:18:49.666 --> 00:18:51.001
FIRST TIME THAT I EVER MET HER.

00:18:51.001 --> 00:18:52.002
I ASKED HER A LOT OF

00:18:52.002 --> 00:18:53.704
QUESTIONS, BUT SHE TOLD ME

00:18:53.704 --> 00:18:54.905
THAT SHE’D LOST ALL HER

00:18:54.905 --> 00:18:57.007
MEMORIES AND...

00:18:57.007 --> 00:19:01.344
MISS CELTY?

00:19:01.344 --> 00:19:02.245
&gt;&gt; WOULD YOU BE WILLING TO LET

00:19:02.245 --> 00:19:03.613
ME SEE HER?

00:19:03.613 --> 00:19:05.281
&gt;&gt; WELL, I DON’T KNOW.

00:19:05.281 --> 00:19:06.582
I MEAN, SHE DOES SEEM PRETTY

00:19:06.582 --> 00:19:07.617
FREAKED OUT BY YOU.

00:19:07.617 --> 00:19:08.884
YOU DID CHASE HER DOWN KIND

00:19:08.884 --> 00:19:14.590
OF HARD YESTERDAY.

00:19:14.590 --> 00:19:16.526
&gt;&gt; I NEED TO SEE THIS GIRL, NO

00:19:16.526 --> 00:19:17.960
MATTER WHAT.

00:19:17.960 --> 00:19:18.894
MAYBE YOU CAN CLEAR UP ANY

00:19:18.894 --> 00:19:23.365
FALSE IMPRESSIONS?

00:19:23.365 --> 00:19:25.835
&gt;&gt; I’LL DO MY BEST.

00:19:25.835 --> 00:19:28.037
&gt;&gt; [gulping]

00:19:28.037 --> 00:19:30.004
[sighs]

00:19:30.004 --> 00:19:31.406
NOTHIN’ LIKE SOME FRUITY MILK

00:19:31.406 --> 00:19:32.607
IN THE AFTERNOON.

00:19:32.607 --> 00:19:33.842
&gt;&gt; I DON’T KNOW ABOUT YOU, BUT

00:19:33.842 --> 00:19:35.510
FOR ME, THIS IS A SURE SIGN THAT

00:19:35.510 --> 00:19:36.411
SHE’S TURNING INTO A REAL

00:19:36.411 --> 00:19:37.979
BIRI BIRI HEROINE!

00:19:37.979 --> 00:19:39.614
&gt;&gt; NO, NO, NO, THE ONLY REAL

00:19:39.614 --> 00:19:41.615
HEROINE IS GONNA BE HIMEGAMI!

00:19:45.719 --> 00:19:49.590
&gt;&gt; HMM? HMM.

00:19:49.590 --> 00:19:52.293
[tires screeching]

00:19:52.293 --> 00:19:54.328
[shouting]

00:19:54.328 --> 00:19:55.295
&gt;&gt; CHILL, DUDE.

00:19:55.295 --> 00:19:56.396
[screams]

00:19:56.396 --> 00:19:57.998
[thud]

00:19:57.998 --> 00:20:00.600
WHAT THE HELL’S GOIN’ ON?

00:20:00.600 --> 00:20:02.035
&gt;&gt; THAT BASTARD.

00:20:02.035 --> 00:20:04.938
WHAT HE DID...

00:20:04.938 --> 00:20:06.073
HE KICKED UP A ROCK AND HIT MY

00:20:06.073 --> 00:20:07.040
VAN!

00:20:07.040 --> 00:20:07.740
[tires screeching]

00:20:07.740 --> 00:20:08.708
[exclamations]

00:20:08.708 --> 00:20:09.942
&gt;&gt; CALM DOWN, SABURO!

00:20:09.942 --> 00:20:11.344
&gt;&gt; YOU WON’T GET AWAY WITH THIS!

00:20:11.344 --> 00:20:12.011
&gt;&gt; THAT’S A RED LIGHT.

00:20:12.011 --> 00:20:13.913
RED LIGHT! RED LIGHT!

00:20:13.913 --> 00:20:15.382
[tires screech]

00:20:15.382 --> 00:20:17.083
&gt;&gt; JUST GIVE ME A MINUTE, OKAY?

00:20:17.083 --> 00:20:18.417
I WANT TO GO INSIDE AND EXPLAIN

00:20:18.417 --> 00:20:19.886
THINGS.

00:20:19.886 --> 00:20:21.620
I’M AFRAID SHE MIGHT THINK THAT

00:20:21.620 --> 00:20:23.455
I BETRAYED HER IF SHE SEES YOU

00:20:23.455 --> 00:20:24.991
GUYS BEFORE I TELL HER WHAT’S

00:20:24.991 --> 00:20:26.458
REALLY GOING ON.

00:20:26.458 --> 00:20:29.695
&gt;&gt; I UNDERSTAND.

00:20:29.695 --> 00:20:31.430
&gt;&gt; HE SURE IS A CAUTIOUS BOY,

00:20:31.430 --> 00:20:37.335
ISN’T HE?

00:20:37.335 --> 00:20:41.572
&gt;&gt; HUH?

00:20:41.572 --> 00:20:44.542
[groans]

00:20:44.542 --> 00:20:45.710
&gt;&gt; YOU KNOW, THIS WAS THE FIRST

00:20:45.710 --> 00:20:47.045
TIME I’VE ACTUALLY HEARD YOUR

00:20:47.045 --> 00:20:47.978
REAL NAME.

00:20:47.978 --> 00:20:49.013
I HAD NO IDEA THAT YOU WERE A

00:20:49.013 --> 00:20:50.681
FOREIGNER.

00:20:50.681 --> 00:20:52.417
&gt;&gt; LIAR.

00:20:52.417 --> 00:20:53.718
THROW ANOTHER ROCK AT MY HORSE,

00:20:53.718 --> 00:20:55.986
AND I’LL MAKE YOU SWALLOW IT.

00:20:55.986 --> 00:20:58.422
&gt;&gt; WOW. IT’S A HORSE.

00:20:58.422 --> 00:21:00.090
WHO KNEW?

00:21:00.090 --> 00:21:03.060
HEY, WHAT DO YOU THINK?

00:21:03.060 --> 00:21:04.494
THIS IS TAKING LONGER THAN IT

00:21:04.494 --> 00:21:07.531
SHOULD, RIGHT?

00:21:07.531 --> 00:21:09.098
&gt;&gt; CLEANING SERVICE?

00:21:09.098 --> 00:21:11.735
IN THIS RUNDOWN PLACE?

00:21:11.735 --> 00:21:13.937
[gasps] OH, NO.

00:21:13.937 --> 00:21:15.371
&gt;&gt; [moans]

00:21:15.371 --> 00:21:16.973
&gt;&gt; ALL RIGHT, I’M GONNA MAKE

00:21:16.973 --> 00:21:18.808
THIS REAL EASY FOR YA.

00:21:18.808 --> 00:21:20.076
ALL YA GOTTA DO IS TELL US

00:21:20.076 --> 00:21:22.411
WHERE YOU’RE HIDING THE GIRL.

00:21:22.411 --> 00:21:23.412
&gt;&gt; THIS HAIR THAT I FOUND IN

00:21:23.412 --> 00:21:24.947
YOUR FUTON LOOKS TO ME LIKE A

00:21:24.947 --> 00:21:26.382
GIRL’S HAIR.

00:21:26.382 --> 00:21:28.951
&gt;&gt; PLEASE! I REALLY DON’T KNOW!

00:21:28.951 --> 00:21:31.153
JUST--JUST LET ME GO, OKAY?

00:21:31.153 --> 00:21:32.388
&gt;&gt; WE CAN’T DO THAT NOW THAT

00:21:32.388 --> 00:21:34.022
YOU’VE SEEN OUR FACES.

00:21:34.022 --> 00:21:35.423
BEST THING FOR US TO DO WOULD

00:21:35.423 --> 00:21:39.094
BE TO KILL YOU RIGHT HERE.

00:21:39.094 --> 00:21:43.665
&gt;&gt; SOMEONE’S COMING.

00:21:43.665 --> 00:21:49.537
&gt;&gt; OH, THANK GOD, I’M SAVED.

00:21:49.537 --> 00:21:50.572
&gt;&gt; THERE’S NO NEED TO FOLLOW

00:21:50.572 --> 00:21:51.406
THEM.

00:21:51.406 --> 00:21:52.407
I KNOW WHERE THEY’RE FROM.

00:21:52.407 --> 00:21:54.075
I’VE SEEN THAT VAN BEFORE.

00:21:54.075 --> 00:21:55.710
CHANCES ARE PRETTY GOOD YAGIRI

00:21:55.710 --> 00:21:57.945
PHARMACEUTICALS SENT THEM.

00:21:57.945 --> 00:22:00.447
&gt;&gt; A PHARMACEUTICAL COMPANY?

00:22:00.447 --> 00:22:01.115
&gt;&gt; YEP.

00:22:01.115 --> 00:22:02.516
IT’S A DYING BEHEMOTH OF A

00:22:02.516 --> 00:22:03.817
COMPANY THAT’S ABOUT TO BE

00:22:03.817 --> 00:22:04.618
BOUGHT OUT BY A FOREIGN

00:22:04.618 --> 00:22:06.553
INVESTOR.

00:22:06.553 --> 00:22:07.788
&gt;&gt; THE GIRL WITH THE SCAR ON

00:22:07.788 --> 00:22:09.456
HER NECK...

00:22:09.456 --> 00:22:11.458
THE DULLAHAN...

00:22:11.458 --> 00:22:13.426
THE DISAPPEARANCES...

00:22:13.426 --> 00:22:15.595
MIKA HARIMA...

00:22:15.595 --> 00:22:18.098
SEIJI YAGIRI...

00:22:18.098 --> 00:22:20.133
HUMAN TRAFFICKING...

00:22:20.133 --> 00:22:22.135
AND THEN THE DOLLARS.

00:22:31.977 --> 00:22:34.013
&gt;&gt; WHAT’S HE DOING?

00:22:34.013 --> 00:22:35.881
&gt;&gt; I DIDN’T WANT TO BE NORMAL.

00:22:35.881 --> 00:22:37.216
&gt;&gt; HONESTLY, I ONLY HALF

00:22:37.216 --> 00:22:41.620
BELIEVED THIS WAS TRUE.

00:22:41.620 --> 00:22:43.455
&gt;&gt; I NEED A BIG FAVOR.

00:22:43.455 --> 00:22:44.856
I’M HOPING YOU GUYS CAN HELP ME

00:22:44.856 --> 00:22:46.090
OUT.

00:22:46.090 --> 00:22:47.225
I WANTED MY LIFE TO BE

00:22:47.225 --> 00:22:49.728
DIFFERENT FROM EVERYONE ELSE.

00:22:49.728 --> 00:22:51.963
ALL RIGHT, I THINK ALL MY CARDS

00:22:51.963 --> 00:22:53.131
ARE IN ORDER NOW.

00:22:53.131 --> 00:22:54.598
&gt;&gt; [laughs]

00:22:54.598 --> 00:22:55.633
&gt;&gt; THAT’S WHY...

00:22:55.633 --> 00:22:56.935
&gt;&gt; AND JACKPOT.

00:22:56.935 --> 00:22:58.836
&gt;&gt; I DECIDED TO.

00:22:58.836 --> 00:23:01.839
&gt;&gt; ♪ [singing in Japanese] ♪

00:23:01.839 --> 00:23:09.880
♪ ♪

00:24:28.588 --> 00:24:30.056
&gt;&gt; I DIDN’T WANT TO BE NORMAL.

00:24:30.056 --> 00:24:32.156
I WANTED MY LIFE TO BE DIFFERENT

00:24:32.156 --> 00:24:34.156
FROM EVERYONE ELSE, BUT I NEVER

00:24:34.156 --> 00:24:35.422
WOULD HAVE THOUGHT THAT THIS ONE

00:24:35.422 --> 00:24:37.756
SIMPLE WISH WOULD AFFECT SO MANY

00:24:37.756 --> 00:24:38.822
PEOPLE.

00:24:38.822 --> 00:24:42.056
NEXT TIME, STORM AND STRESS.

